@startuml Fintan-contents_case-studies

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as Backend
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as CICD
database "Database" as DB
queue "Message Queue" as MQ
participant "Monitoring Service" as Monitor

User -> Frontend : Interact with UI
Frontend -> Backend : API Request
Backend -> DB : Query/Update Data
Backend -> MQ : Publish Message
MQ -> Backend : Consume Message
Backend -> Frontend : API Response
Frontend -> User : Update UI

CICD -> Frontend : Deploy
CICD -> Backend : Deploy
CICD -> DB : Apply Schema Changes

Backend -> Monitor : Send Metrics
Frontend -> Monitor : Send Logs

@enduml